      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically robust example of the legendary S54-powered platform. The high-revving 3.2L inline-six delivers linear power through individual throttle bodies and optimized Double VANOS variable valve timing. Power is sent to the rear wheels via a precise Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory M-variable differential lock. Significant preventative maintenance has been addressed, including subframe reinforcement and a recent valve clearance adjustment, ensuring structural integrity and valvetrain precision. The chassis retains its signature balance with a MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear suspension setup. While the exterior shows honest wear consistent with enthusiast use, the drivetrain and suspension geometry remain dialed for spirited driving.",
